sequenceDiagram
  participant Svc as Domain service
  participant OB as NotificationOutbox
  participant Disp as Outbox processor
  participant Email as IEmailProvider
  Svc->>OB: Enqueue idempotent message
  Disp->>OB: Claim pending rows
  Disp->>Email: Send (dev SMTP or NotConfigured)
  alt success
    Disp->>OB: Mark Sent
  else failure
    Disp->>OB: Retry / Failed with limit
  end
